page.title: 09Family Life
page.content: {Isabel's Day.} I waken after eight.I do not have breakfast.My mum takes me to school in the car.I do Language till half past ten.We go out to play for half an hour,then we do Maths until twelve o'clock,then we have a Reading Time.At 12.25 we wash our hands,set the tables and have dinner.I go out to play again.At half past one we come in and do Art with the Art Specialist until 3.25 when we tidy up and go home.When I get home I watch T.V. until six o'clock.Then I have my tea.When I am finished I go and play outside for a while and then I come in and watch T.V.Before I go to bed I have a supper of bran biscuits and cheese, and a drink of lemonade.
